AshleyRitchie
Preston, UK28 contributions
Ginger Junk Ha Long Bay
Beautiful boat with old world charm. A trip to Ha Long Bay on the Ha Long Ginger is like stepping back in time. The boat is beautifully decorated and well equipped, the lunch on board was as good as any 5* restaurant. The bay its self is like entering a alternate planet lost in time. The bay people are happy to welcome you into their world and proud to show off their homes & families. The evening dinner in the cave was spectacular with a unique setting and top quality food. The floating islands and deep green waters makes a trip to the bay unforgettable. I would highly recommend the Ginger Junk for quality & customer service.
